<br>
我不知道如何才能表达对它的喜爱，这是一张我反复（从头至尾）聆听至少上百次的专辑。从单曲的质量/单曲间的连接和呼应都很难让我挑出毛病，甚至专辑封面都无可挑剔。
<p>Something 是其中我最喜欢的单曲（之一），它是我心中最好的情歌</p>
<iframe allow="autoplay *; encrypted-media *;" frameborder="0" height="150" style="width:100%;max-width:660px;overflow:hidden;background:transparent;" sandbox="allow-forms allow-popups allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-storage-access-by-user-activation allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation" src="https://embed.music.apple.com/us/album/something/1441164426?i=1441164582"></iframe>
<h2 id="ok-computer---radiohead">OK Computer - Radiohead</h2>
<iframe allow="autoplay *; encrypted-media *;" frameborder="0" height="450" style="width:100%;max-width:660px;overflow:hidden;background:transparent;" sandbox="allow-forms allow-popups allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-storage-access-by-user-activation allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation" src="https://embed.music.apple.com/us/album/ok-computer/1097861387"></iframe>
<h2 id="getzgilberto---stan-getz-joão-gilberto">Getz/Gilberto - Stan Getz, João Gilberto</h2>
<iframe allow="autoplay *; encrypted-media *;" frameborder="0" height="450" style="width:100%;max-width:660px;overflow:hidden;background:transparent;" sandbox="allow-forms allow-popups allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-storage-access-by-user-activation allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation" src="https://embed.music.apple.com/us/album/getz-gilberto/1422655717"></iframe>
<p>我认为 <strong>Bossa Nova</strong> 是一种伟大的音乐流派，而它的作者， <strong>Antônio Carlos Jobim</strong> ，则是神一般的存在</p>
<p>















  
  
      
      
